Rules.auto_name: Derive AvailableBalance as sum(CHECKING_TRANSList.Total where PendingFlag = 0)
Derive CreditLimit as parentcopy(fk_checking_valid_credit1.MaxCreditLimit)
Derive CurrentBalance as sum(CHECKING_TRANSList.Total)
Derive Deposits as sum(CHECKING_TRANSList.DepositAmt)
Derive ItemCount as count(CHECKING_TRANSList where WithdrawlAmt > 0)
Derive Withdrawls as sum(CHECKING_TRANSList.WithdrawlAmt)
Derive null as sum(null.null)

Rules.rule_text2: You cannot have both a withdraw and deposit on the same transaction line

Rules.auto_name: Derive Total as return row.DepositAmt - row.WithdrawlAmt
Derive CheckingAcctBal as sum(CHECKINGList.AvailableBalance)
Derive SavingsAcctBal as sum(SAVINGSList.AvailableBalance)
Derive TotalBalance as return row.CheckingAcctBal + row.SavingsAcctBal
